scenario_text.value:
You’re still hanging around? You’re too weak
to be here on your own.

Get your to brother protect you. Ah, but he
isn’t here now, huh? Too bad...

I, I don’t need Kaito.... I can do just fine
on my own...

Haha, you mean your spirit power? You know
that’s a total sham.

You’re just ignoring your insignificance.
Just accept it. Let yourself be protected.

Unnngh... No, stop... I don’t wanna be
protected forever...
Don’t worry, Miu. This Syakomon is a phony.

The Syakomon that hangs out with you would
never deny your power.

He knows how strong you are. There’s no way
he’d call you insignificant.
Oh... Yeah, you’re right. But then, this’s...?

(He said such awful things to Miu... If Kaito
were here he’d be a fine paste on the floor.)
